Cookie management

   When you browse our websites or open the emails we send you,
   information may be recorded or read on your device or browser, with
   your consent. You can check or uncheck the options below, according to
   your preferences.
     * Technical cookies are necessary to ensure the optimal functioning
       of our websites. They play a role in particular in security,
       ergonomics and language choice. As a result, they are constantly
       activated.
       [ ]
     * I accept the saving and reading of cookies to allow Crit'Air to
       analyse my browsing and tracking the visitors to its websites.
       [ ]

